description: Join Emmy and Annie award winner Rob Paulsen as he talks about his experiences in voice acting! Visit www.RobPaulsenLive.com for more information!
title: Talkin Toons with Rob Paulsen - Weekly Voice Acting and Voice Over Tips

episodes.title: Dante Basco
episodes.description: Dante Basco (Lost Boys, Hook, Avatar: The Last Air Bender) joins host Rob Paulsen to talk about starting as a breakdancer in San Francisco to acting on film and voice acting. Plus, Zuko takes a spin as Belloq from Raiders of the Lost Ark.

episodes.title: David Hayter
episodes.description: David Hayter (Metal Gear, X-Men, X2, Watchmen) joins host Rob Paulsen to talk about voicing Solid Snake in the Metal Gear series and screenwriting in Hollywood. Plus, Solid Snake takes on the role of Vince in a scene from Heat.

episodes.title: Jonny Cruz
episodes.description: Rob Paulsen, one of the most accomplished and well-known voice actors of our time, sits down with various other voice actors to discuss their experiences! And yes, of course, there'll be plenty of voice acting games from script-reading to re-enacting famous film scenes with cartoon character voices.

On this episode of Talkin' Toons, Rob Paulsen is joined by the legendary Nancy Cartwright! As the voice of Bart Simpson and a good personal friend of Rob, the two talk on their experiences, read scripts, and more!

Get access to the video portion TWO WEEKS before the podcast by joining team Alpha!

episodes.title: Phil LaMarr
episodes.description:
On this episode of Talkin' Toons, Rob Paulsen is joined by the great Phil LaMarr! The two discuss their experiences, do a script reading from Futurama, and more!

Get access to the video portion TWO WEEKS before the podcast by joining team Alpha!

episodes.title: Nolan North
episodes.description:
Today on Talkin' Toons... Nolan frickin' North! Yes, that Nolan North. The Nolan North from Uncharted and many, many other great things.

Get access to the video portion TWO WEEKS before the podcast by joining team Alpha!

episodes.title: Matthew Mercer
episodes.description:
Matthew Mercer has developed an enormous following across Overwatch, Critical Role, and more. Now, he sits down with Rob Paulsen to discuss everything voice acting!

Get access to the video portion TWO WEEKS before the podcast by joining team Alpha!

episodes.title: TMNT Villains
episodes.description:
Rob Paulsen is joined by Pat Fraley, Renae Jacobs, and Pete Renaday who all voiced characters in the Teenage Mutant Ninja Turtles!

Get access to the video portion TWO WEEKS before the podcast by joining team Alpha!

episodes.title: Teenage Mutant Ninja Turtles
episodes.description:
They're heroes in a half-shell and they're green. And the original voice of the turtles Cam Clarke, Townsend Coleman, and Barry Gordon are here talking with Rob Paulsen!

Get access to the video portion TWO WEEKS before the podcast by joining team Alpha!

episodes.title: Billy West
episodes.description:
Rob Paulsen travels in time and space to talk toons with Billy West (Futurama, Ren & Stimpy, and many, many more)!

Get access to the video portion TWO WEEKS before the podcast by joining team Alpha!

episodes.title: Randy Rogel
episodes.description:
On this episode of Talkin' Toons, Rob Paulsen is joined by Randy Rogel (writer for Animaniacs, Batman & Mr. Freeze: SubZero, and more) to do some duets on the piano, discuss their experiences, and more!

Get access to the video portion TWO WEEKS before the podcast by joining team Alpha!

episodes.title: Tara Strong
episodes.description:
Rob Paulsen meets his match with guest Tara Strong, the voice of many, many characters including Bubbles, Timmy Turner, and more!

Get access to the video portion TWO WEEKS before the podcast by joining team Alpha!

episodes.title: Talkin' Batman with Kevin Conroy, Paul Dini, and Alan Burnett
episodes.description:
Rob Paulsen is joined by guests Kevin Conroy, Paul Dini, and Alan Burnett to talk their experiences, read scripts with their character voices, and more!

Get access to the video portion TWO WEEKS before the podcast by joining team Alpha!

episodes.title: Who's On First with Maurice LaMarche
episodes.description:
Rob Paulsen has brought his podcast to the video format with Talkin' Toons! On this first episode, Rob is joined by Maurice LaMarche! The two discuss their industry, read a script in the voice of Pinky and the Brain, and more!

Get access to the video portion TWO WEEKS before the podcast by joining team Alpha!
